Title: WATO pages with host links: Fixed recently introduced performance problem
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: wato
Date: 1612532414
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 1.6.0p21

Version p19 tried to speed up some WATO pages showing tables with lots of host links.
This fix backfired and slowed down the system even more.
This commit fixes the broken fix.
Especially rule listings with many host conditions should now be displayed much faster.
